New generation Advanced Resource Connector (ARC) grid middleware

- Requirements for build from source tree
    - g++
    - libxml2
    - glibmm
    - doxygen
    - pkg-config
    - automake
    - autoconf
    - libtool

- Optional requirements
    - swig (>1.3.28)
    - java sdk for Java bindings
    - python-dev for Python bindings
